      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIOGO KEEPING (4) is a handy dog who jumped from box 7 last time out and scored by 0.8 lengths at Gawler (22.27). Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Expected to go well again. BUSTER BRADY (1) is better than last start when sixth (20.46) from Box 6 at Angle Park over 342m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and five minor placings from 11 starts. Key player if finds best. VICTORY CLUB (2) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Angle Park over 530m behind Amron Tiger (31.79) in a Invitation. Was in the money prior to that. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Can figure in the finish. SON OF MAPLE (6) game in defeat when in the minors last start in a handy 19.68. One of the chances.",
